timelineItems.text: Let's get this game started! GO FCD!! Thanks to @JimmySlaughter for the shot! @FCDallas #DTID #RedFor90 #host http://t.co/AvtFe5eqGC

timelineItems.name: Chip Thomas
timelineItems.text: So instead of getting a min of 4 pts in two games..we may walk away with 1. Somebody tell me the logic of sitting starters???? #Rapids96

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Nick LaBrocca (Colorado Rapids).
Jair Benitez (FC Dallas) wins a free kick in the defensive half.

timelineItems.name: Thor Morgan
timelineItems.text: Pablo needs to use a sub. Nothing doing with the #Rapids96 right now #DALvCOL

timelineItems.comment: Hand ball by Tesho Akindele (FC Dallas).
Charles Eloundou (Colorado Rapids) wins a free kick on the left wing.
Foul by Je-Vaughn Watson (FC Dallas).
Delay in match Raúl Fernández (FC Dallas) because of an injury.

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: Great ball from Serna finds Eloundou behind, but Fernandez on it quickly and holds. Now he's down, trainer attending. #Rapids96 #DALvCOL

timelineItems.comment: Delay over. They are ready to continue.

timelineItems.name: Chris Bianchi
timelineItems.text: Torres on in the 88th for Jose Mari- first appearance for Torres since May 7th.

timelineItems.name: Toe---Moss
timelineItems.text: “@ColoradoRapids: A minimum of six minutes added. #Rapids96 still have time...” Thats enough time to win it

timelineItems.comment: Offside, FC Dallas. Andrew Jacobson tries a through ball, but Fabian Castillo is caught offside.
Foul by Marlon Hairston (Colorado Rapids).
Blas Pérez (FC Dallas) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Attempt missed. Deshorn Brown (Colorado Rapids) left footed shot from the right side of the box misses to the left. Assisted by Marvell Wynne.
Stephen Keel (FC Dallas) wins a free kick in the defensive half.
Foul by Dillon Serna (Colorado Rapids).
Attempt missed. Marlon Hairston (Colorado Rapids) right footed shot from outside the box is high and wide to the right. Assisted by Dillon Powers.

timelineItems.name: Thomas Howard
timelineItems.text: And the winless streak comes to an end!!! #FCD wins 3-2 #FCDvCOL #DTID

timelineItems.name: Drew Epperley
timelineItems.text: Ball game. First win in a long time for #FCDallas

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, FC Dallas 3, Colorado Rapids 2.

timelineItems.desc: Dan Haiek and Armchair Analyst Matt Doyle preview the Saturday evening match between FC Dallas and the Colorado Rapids. Does Dallas have an advantage thanks to Oscar Pareja's familiarity with the Colorado players? Is FCD's best attacking strategy route 1? Find out Saturday at 830pm ET on MLS Live.
